,"src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17467,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/04\/judge-deeds-not-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":24373,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Judgment: We judge outward deeds, not inner-states","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 4, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn 'Utbah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, people were judged by revelation in the time of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and the revelation has ceased. We only judge now what is manifested outwardly of your deeds.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24330,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/01\/umar-ikhlaas-allah-take-care\/","url_meta":{"origin":24373,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Sincerity: Allah takes care of those who are sincere","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amir al-Sha\u2019bi reported: Umar ibn Al-Khattab wrote to Abu Musa, may Allah be pleased with them both, saying, \u201cWhoever purifies his intention, Allah will take care of his affairs between people. Whoever embellishes for people what Allah knows is not in his heart, Allah Almighty will disgrace him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dail